 surely, it could only go up from here on. Maybe another gold medal, maybe even a unprecedented double-digit tally. The hope was high, as was the belief.And came back to india with only two medals. That to for women’s  Sindhu, Sakshi shine as India end campaign with two medals out of 119 strong contenders  so in which depart</p>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"57fb20172c85f\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:2;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"89f5b03d-e36e-4857-832d-ae7caddc6410\";s:5:\"style\";a:3:{s:7:\"padding\";s:19:\"20px 20px 20px 20px\";s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:12:\"border_color\";s:7:\"#efefef\";}}}}s:5:\"grids\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}}s:10:\"grid_cells\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:6:\"weight\";i:1;}}}'),(1566,480,'panels_data','a:3:{s:7:\"widgets\";a:3:{i:0;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:45:\"How will India win medals at the 2020 Tokyo ?\";s:4:\"text\";s:823:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-451\" src=\"http://www.letzpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/tk2-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"Web\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />India went to the Olympic Games in Rio with its biggest contingent yet and more expectations than ever. The 100-plus strong squad, with big names and experienced contenders, were set to create history with a record haul.  If the country could claim six medals at London 2012 – with two of the being silver – surely, it could only go up from here on. Maybe another gold medal, maybe even a unprecedented double-digit tally. The hope was high, as was the belief.And came back to india with only two medals. That to for women’s  Sindhu, Sakshi shine as India end campaign with two medals out of 119 strong contenders  so in which depart</p><p> </p>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";