6/10/tk2-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"Web\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />India went to the Olympic Games in Rio with its biggest contingent yet and more expectations than ever. The 100-plus strong squad, with big names and experienced contenders, were set to create history with a record haul.  If the country could claim six medals at London 2012 – with two of the being silver – surely, it could only go up from here on. Maybe another gold medal, maybe even a unprecedented double-digit tally. The hope was high, as was the belief.And came back to india with only two medals. That to for women’s  Sindhu, Sakshi shine as India end campaign with two medals out of 119 strong contenders  so in which depart.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Sample 2</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-453 alignleft\" src=\"http://www.letzpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/sachin-tendulkar2-1-300x167.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"http://www.letzpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/sachin-tendulkar2-1-300x167.jpg 300w, http://www.letzpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/sachin-tendulkar2-1.jpg 651w\" alt=\"sachin-tendulkar2\" width=\"300\" height=\"167\" />\r\n\r\nThe Mumbai Cricket Association has accepted Sachin Tendulkar’s suggestion to have 14 players in a side at inter-school tournaments. While only 11 players will field at any point, the new rule allows for the players in the squad to be used for batting and bowling by way of rolling substitutions.\r\n\r\nPV Shetty, the MCA joint-secretary, confirmed that Tendulkar’s suggestion had been approved and would be implemented from the upcoming season starting with the Harris Shield on November 11. The new guidelines have also been accepted by the Mumbai Schools’ Sports Association.\r\n\r\n<!--democracy-->\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">.democracy:after{content:\'\';display:table;clear:both}.democracy ul li,.democracy ul{background:none;padding:0;margin:0}.democracy ul li:before{display:none}.democr